Package com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.importer.rf2.util

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EffectiveTimeBaseTransactionAggregatorSupplier
    Supplies transaction aggregator based on SNOMED CT specific effective times.
    ImportUtil
    Provides utility methods for setting up and running importers.
    Rf2FileModifier
    Contains utility methods for modifying incoming RF2 files.
    RF2ReleaseRefSetFileCollector
    Based on the import configuration this helper class collects all the available refset files which have to be imported.
    SnomedRefSetNameCollector
    Class for getting textual representation of a SNOMED CT reference set (based on the reference set ID) at import time.
